result.title: No Country for Old Men: Josh Brolin's Unauthorized Behind the Scenes
result.overview: A piece featuring additional cast and crew interview snippets and behind-the-scenes footage. We find comments from Joel and Ethan Coen, Jones, Bardem, Graf, Brolin, Macdonald, production supervisor Karen Getchell, associate producer Dave Diliberto and actor Woody Harrelson.

result.title: Heath Ledger: A Hollywood Tragedy
result.overview: A look back at Heath Ledger's outstanding career that was cut short by his sad & unexpected death. Family and friends, fans and experts alike mourn the loss of Hollywood's talented star who had so much more to give.

result.title: Alemanha, Ano Zero
result.overview: Vivendo num apartamento bombardeado com o pai doente e dois irmãos mais velhos, o jovem Edmund passa boa parte do tempo sem supervisão. Ele se envolve nos esquemas do mercado negro de um grupo de adolescentes e é influenciado por um ex-professor simpatizante do nazismo.

result.title: Japan
result.overview: Code name Japan is a contract killer on a job. Accustomed to staying in hotels, Japan finds himself jet-lagged in the middle of the night and forced to eat in the hotel restaurant, room service being closed. There, he meets a man, Alfred. Alfred was recently evicted from their marital home by his now ex-wife and now lives at the hotel. A loner befriends another loner, and their unexpected friendship leads their faith to a twist and turn ending ...

result.title: Week-End à Francesa
result.overview: Um fim de semana supostamente idílico de uma viagem para o campo se transforma em um pesadelo sem fim de engarrafamentos, revolução, canibalismo e assassinato, quando a sociedade burguesa francesa começa a desmoronar sob o peso de suas próprias preocupações como consumidores.

result.title: The Pig
result.overview: In this live-action, Oscar-nominated short from Denmark, Asbjorn is a patient admitted to a Danish hospital, who quickly warms to a painting of a whimsical pig hung on the walls. It becomes a source of comfort and solace for him - until another patient has it removed by request (Written by Nathan Southern, Rovi)
